@startuml 22-ask-new-session
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Ask New Session

actor User
participant "AskModePage" as UI
participant "AskSessionService" as SVC

User -> UI: tap "+" (newBtn)
alt messages.length > 0
    UI -> UI: open confirm dialog
    User -> UI: confirm
end
UI -> SVC: messages.set([])
UI -> SVC: sessionId.set(newGuid())
UI -> UI: re-render greeting only
UI --> User: chat cleared to greeting state

... later ...
User -> UI: type new question, send
UI -> UI: POST /api/ask\n{ sessionId: newGuid }
note right of UI
  New sessionId isolates
  conversation memory server-side
end note

@enduml
